<h6 id="no-point-in-stuffing-the-boiler">NO POINT IN STUFFING THE BOILER</h6>

<p>After 11 days of this half-fast my weight is 68.5 kg (151 lbs), a small loss of 1.5 kg (3.30 lbs). But I can already feel in myself a renewed vigour, in spite of having consumed so little food. It is therefore the sign that the assimilation of food by the organism is better than it was before. This confirms for me what Mr. Mosseri said : ‚Äú_There is no point in eating a lot to obtain energy for the body. It is much more important ‚Äì vital even ‚Äì  to properly assimilate what is consumed.</p>

<p>To use an image, I would say that stuffing the boiler if it doesn‚Äôt draw well is done in vain. It is preferable to have the pipes swept (detoxified) beforehand. ‚Äì  Edward J., Engineer at Sarrebourg.</p>

