      &lt;li&gt;You really believe that Doctor ?&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Yes,  it‚Äôs the <em>Immurel</em>.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ol&gt;</p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>42

I didn‚Äôt dare reveal that I had stopped taking this drug six months previously ! Now I had&lt;br&gt;
  trapped him I was embarrassed.&lt;br&gt;
  Then I again pretended to be stupid,  which had worked very well. I asked him :
&lt;ol&gt;
